No. 11-5826. Janet Marcusse, Petitioner v. United States District Court for the Western District of Michigan. 565 U.S. 936, 132 S. Ct. 388,

181 L. Ed. 2d 244,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6330. October 3, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
